Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Total time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Checklist Completed after the execution of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total waiting time to the SW-Checklist Completed following SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and Plagiarism Originality Report Completed in variants that include both activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average time until SW-Checklist Completed is performed after SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in submissions leading to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in cases that proceed to reviewer assignment (e.g., SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and the end of case where activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers occurs

Name: Time of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in variants that include checklist deadline reminders (e.g., SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days occurs

Name: Average time it takes SW-Checklist Completed after SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion compared to the time it takes Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation after SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Total time from SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in multi-round revision cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Minimum time for SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion in cases that eventually reach SW-EIC Accept
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and the end of the case

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and SW-Initial Reviewer Selection in variants where checklist completion precedes reviewer selection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion and Manuscript Export Succeeded in high-performance variants (performance < 500000)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'
